00:18:14.910 --> 00:18:15.500
Sa Kisame!

00:18:15.830 --> 00:18:16.820
Magnakaw muna ng Dormant Dragon Sword!

00:18:16.900 --> 00:18:17.890
Maari na nating planuhin ito pagkatapos nito!

00:18:22.390 --> 00:18:23.020
Tiyo Qidao?

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:24.980
Miyembro ba iyon ng pamilya Xie?

00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:26.410
Noon,

00:18:26.800 --> 00:18:28.260
ang pamilyang Su, na siyang pinakamalakas na pamilya sa tatlo,

00:18:28.830 --> 00:18:30.260
ay lubusang natalo

00:18:30.430 --> 00:18:31.700
ni Mu Ciling lamang.

00:18:39.040 --> 00:18:40.460
Dahil nakuha ko ang Dormant Dragon Sword,

00:18:41.040 --> 00:18:42.060
pwede ba akong maging

00:18:43.150 --> 00:18:44.330
ang susunod na Patriarch?

00:18:45.110 --> 00:18:46.300
Masyado pang maaga para diyan.

00:18:47.350 --> 00:18:48.650
Sa iyo lang ito kung kaya mo

00:18:49.280 --> 00:18:50.300
dalhin ito sa iyo.

